Based on the short story by Stephen King. After the crash landing of a Fed spacecraft on a strange, desert planet, only crew members Rand and Billy Shapiro survive. The men stare out over the sand dunes and Rand remarks on how the planet is similar to a beach. Billy dismisses this and begins to find a way off the planet by using the thought to be broken beacon. Rand, who is going insane, refuses to move from the dune on which he is sitting, or to drink water.
